description: The Irish town is celebrating the US election victory of Joe Biden, who has roots in County Louth.
title: Joe Biden: Carlingford celebrates links to US president-elect
title_page: Joe Biden: Carlingford celebrates links to US president-elect - BBC News
maintext: John Owen Finegan said he wished Mr Biden "all the best and the best of health in his new post" and said "we'd like to see him back in the near future".
